title: 2020 Week 1 Recap
itunes:title: 2020 Week 1 Recap
description:
It's finally here! A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal recap every single game from Week 1 starting off with Tom Brady's debut as a Buc (3:47), Aaron Rodgers playing lights out (11:17), and Cam Newton's Patriots (24:15). Yeah, I said it! We take you through each game including the Sunday Night nail biter between the Rams and Cowboys.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
